{"title_page": "Silvia Carolina Mazariegos", "text_new": "{{notability|1=Biographies|date=April 2020}}\n\n'''Silvia Carolina Mazariegos''' (born 4 April 1961<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q21106323|title=Silvia Carolina Mazariegos|website=www.wikidata.org|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>) is a [[Guatemala]]n [[Woman International Master]] (WIM) since 1987. Her higheat [[Chess rating system|rating]] was 2135 (in April 2005) and she is ranked as Guatemala's 2nd best female player.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://chess-db.com/public/pinfo.jsp?id=7300115|title=Silvia Carolina Mazariegos' chess profile|last=|first=|date=|website=chess DB|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=7300115|title=Mazariegos, Silvia Carolina FIDE Chess Profile - Players Arbiters Trainers|website=ratings.fide.com|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.365chess.com/players/Silvia_Carolina_Mazariegos|title=Silvia Carolina Mazariegos chess games - 365Chess.com|website=www.365chess.com|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://players.chessbase.com/en/player/Mazariegos_%20Silvia%20Carolina|title=Silvia Carolina Mazariegos|last=GmbH|first=ChessBase|website=ChessBase Players|language=en|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Felice|first=Gino Di|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0dBHDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA207&lpg=PA207&dq=Silvia+Carolina+Mazariegos&source=bl&ots=wT-ntSaNb8&sig=ACfU3U2BU2nKK3cCtQsfuIQgIZWdh6KSmw&hl=iw&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiOypr7xNfoAhWGdd8KHWdvDMQ4ChDoATAEegQICxAr#v=onepage&q=Silvia%20Carolina%20Mazariegos&f=false|title=Chess International Titleholders, 1950-2016|date=2018-01-16|publisher=McFarland|isbn=978-1-4766-3361-9|language=en}}</ref>\n\nShe is the champion of the [[Guatemalan Chess Championship|Guatemalan women chess championship]] 22 times in the years: 1981 -1994, 2001, 2002, 2009, 2011, 2014, 2015, 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http